<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“毛克利应该没事的，巴鲁。”巴希拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他很聪明，你也把他教得很好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉沉思着舔了舔一只爪子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我们的确需要一个计划把他救回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，这是个问题。”巴鲁说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为那些猴子不怕我们俩。嘿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他猛地坐起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些猴子很怕卡阿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们去跟他商量商量吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我真的不喜欢跟那条蟒蛇说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不确定他算不算我们的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有……”巴希拉发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他有一双吓人的眼睛。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀，巴希拉。卡阿很狡猾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们去看看他能不能帮我们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉叹了口气。“好吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡阿躺在一块暖和的石头上晒着午后的太阳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他蜷曲着长长的身体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他欣赏着自己新的黄褐相间的皮肤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小心点，巴希拉。”巴鲁边走边小声说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卡阿蜕皮后，总是眼神不太好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，他可能会突然攻击你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡阿不是毒蛇，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他还是很危险。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他能把猎物紧紧缠死。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好啊，卡阿！”巴鲁喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，巴鲁，你怎么来了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们来请你帮忙。”棕熊回答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要找到猴子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这事儿很紧急。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘶嘶嘶。”卡阿懒洋洋地说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我又累又饱，现在没心情追猴子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁看了一眼巴希拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果卡阿不帮他们，怎么办？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，卡阿……”巴希拉咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道猴子们叫你‘无脚黄蚯蚓’吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡阿的双眼闪过一丝愤怒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们叫我蚯蚓？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“差不多是那个意思。”巴希拉回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有时候他们还取笑你。”巴鲁插嘴说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们说你没有牙，说你害怕山羊角。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”卡阿缠紧了身体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他喉咙上的大块肌肉上下起伏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们为什么找猴子？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，你知道，我是一个人类孩子的老师。”巴鲁开始说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他一般很听我的话。可是，有一次，他……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉开始不耐烦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们没时间讲冗长的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“事情是这样的，卡阿。”他插嘴说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些愚蠢的坚果小偷们偷走了那个人类孩子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是个很棒的人类孩子。”巴鲁说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是世上最聪明、勇敢的人类孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我、我们，爱他，卡阿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘶嘶嘶！”卡阿前后动着头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个人类孩子应该和你们在一起，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不是那些猴子，你们是他的家人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以我们来到了这里。”巴希拉说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些猴子在森林里只怕你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265876</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以，我们希望你能帮我们找到他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁接着说道，“求你了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些可怕的猴子不停地叽叽喳喳。”卡阿生气地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们还又傻又懒。”卡阿转向巴希拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些猴子叫我什么？黄鱼？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉低下了头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“叫你黄蚯蚓，还有别的难听的名字。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要去提醒他们说点儿我的好话！”卡阿厉声说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们去哪儿了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们以为你可能知道，卡阿。”巴鲁说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道他们今天搬到森林的另一个地方去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡阿嘶嘶地说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“刚才我听见他们在树梢间大笑。但是……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“向上看！向上看！”上面传来刺耳的叫声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁抬头看去，兰正朝着这边飞来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有一个关于毛克利的消息！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鹰喊道：“那些猴子把他带进了森林深处。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>347089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，他在河那边呢，在猴子城里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>